post_text:
@GovernorVA declared today VIRGINIA IS FOR LEARNERS DAY! Read the proclamation at https://buff.ly/2lpuzUC
MPCS is a lead innovation team in the commonwealth and we love that #VAis4Learners - We'd also like to congratulate those who have been named to our Innovation Cohort. Keep up the great work! 🙌
#VaLIN #MPCSConnects Virginia Department of Education - VDOE

